title: Khloe Kardashian Is Nearly Unrecognizable With Brunette Curls in New KKW Fragrance Campaign
text: The Independent: Sondland (who donated a cool $1 million to Trump campaign and was given the EU ambassador position) testified that he didn't recall being warned by any security expert about pressuring Ukraine for dirt on Biden. Then Dr. Fiona Hill, a security expert on Russia, testified that she herself told Sondland that it was inappropriate, and now Colonel Vindman, an expert on Ukraine issues, also testified that he himself told Sondland that it was inappropriate. Congress should bring Sondland back, and charge him with perjury if he lies again.
description: The reality star appears to have returned to being a brunette in the stunning photos, which were released on Tuesday.
